      • Player

        public Player(int row,
              int col,
              int px,
              int py,
              java.lang.String s,
              int t,
              int mov,
              int gr,
              int gc,
              int pm,
              int snks,
              int lads)
        Player: Constructor of PLayer class
        pre
        pos
        Parameters:
        row - Row position in which the player is going to be created within the matrix.
        col - Column position in which the player is going to be created within the matrix.
        px - Position on the X axis of the player. Used for painting it.
        py - Position on the Y axis of the player. Used for painting it.
        s - Player symbol used for identify it
        t - Assigned turn for playing
        mov - Amount of turns that the player has used
        gr - Number of rows that the board will have.
        gc - Number of columns that the board will have.
        pm - Number of players that the board will have.
        snks - Number of snakes that the board will have.
        lads - Number of ladders that the board will have.
